Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.preprocess.strategies.wsio

Visitors and supporting classes for determining the proper strategy for wsio activities and their message data production or consumption.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeMessageDataStrategyMatcher Interface for matching a def to the strategy used to produce message data
IAeMessageDataStrategyNames Provides the names for the valid strategies for producing and consuming message data
 

Class Summary
AeBaseMessageDataStrategyMatcher Base class for message data consumer and producer strategy matchers.
AeBPWSMessageDataStrategyMatcher Contains the valid strategy patterns for BPEL4WS 1.1 The only valid message data consumer or producer strategy for 1.1 is the message-variable strategy.
AeMessageDataSpec Describes how a wsio activity produces or consumes its message data
AeMessageDataStrategyVisitor Visits each invoke and reply in order to set the strategy hint on the def
AeWSBPELMessageDataProducerStrategyMatcher Contains the valid strategy patterns for WS-BPEL 2.0
